So I&#039;ve been playing {{champion:6}} Since about season 3 now and took him to the jungle in season 4. Since then I continued to master him in the Jungle, and now consider it as a pick in ranked. In all my research I have never found any evidence of another Urgot jungle. I have checked through Youtube, boards, old forums and guide sites but have never found another person playing Urgot in the jungle.

Ill give a quick item build here but feel free to ask me something down below, Ill try answer.
Use {{summoner:11}}  and {{summoner:6}} 
Start with {{item:1039}} + 3x {{item:2003}} 
Get either {{item:1400}} or {{item:1412}} 
Follow that up with a {{item:3071}} 
After this you have a damage option or a tank option
Damage:
{{item:3142}} {{item:3156}} {{item:3812}} 
Tank: 
{{item:3143}} {{item:3026}} {{item:3102}} 
I usually pick up either {{item:3009}} {{item:3111}} {{item:3158}} for boots, depending on how I snowballed. 

Good luck on the rift and let me know how you do
-Donkeytoesness
